ich the President of the United States is involved—occurs in front of his eyes. He is forced to run, while holding evidence that could convict the President.","genre_ids":[80,18,28],"popularity":2.2658,"vote_count":1203,"poster_path":"/izvyt3cxlilhbYwybTOteDWqf99.jpg","release_date":"1997-02-14","vote_average":6.658,"backdrop_path":"/cLftTzGw40BlLw8IggKSWDjKOQo.jpg","original_title":"Absolute Power","original_language":"en"},{"id":74,"adult":false,"title":"War of the Worlds","video":false,"overview":"Ray Ferrier is a divorced dockworker and less-than-perfect father. Soon after his ex-wife and her new husband drop off his teenage son and young daughter for a rare weekend visit, a strange and powerful lightning storm touches down.","genre_ids":[12,53,878],"popularity":9.6095,"vote_count":8978,"poster_path":"/6Biy7R9LfumYshur3YKhpj56MpB.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-28","vote_average":6.531,"backdrop_path":"/bInicBgSHfQiWLbnRT5jxw9Grvm.jpg","original_title":"War of the Worlds","original_language":"en"},{"id":79,"adult":false,"title":"Hero","video":false,"overview":"During China's Warring States period, a district prefect arrives at the palace of Qin Shi Huang, claiming to have killed the three assassins who had made an attempt on the king's life three years ago.","genre_ids":[18,12,28,36],"popularity":5.4344,"vote_count":2436,"poster_path":"/vxgZto2Cz7ILHAlmRXt50I2brB2.jpg","release_date":"2002-12-19","vote_average":7.508,"backdrop_path":"/jDz6RYN3nKYtlo7J9IMvGoJit7B.jpg","original_title":"英雄","original_language":"zh"},{"id":87,"adult":false,"title":"Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom","video":false,"overview":"After arriving in India, Indiana Jones is asked by a desperate village to find a mystical stone. He agrees – and stumbles upon a secret cult plotting a terrible plan in the catacombs of an ancient palace.","genre_ids":[12,28],"popularity":9.179,"vote_count":9952,"poster_path":"/gpdVNUaa4LhRMLfJOPj1AZdhAZ3.jpg","release_date":"1984-05-23","vote_average":7.304,"b