mbers at the Orthanc Tower in Isengard.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":17.7989,"vote_count":23477,"poster_path":"/5VTN0pR8gcqV3EPUHHfMGnJYN9L.jpg","release_date":"2002-12-18","vote_average":8.413,"backdrop_path":"/kWYfW2Re0rUDE6IHhy4CRuKWeFr.jpg","original_title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers","original_language":"en"},{"id":122,"adult":false,"title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King","video":false,"overview":"As armies mass for a final battle that will decide the fate of the world--and powerful, ancient forces of Light and Dark compete to determine the outcome--one member of the Fellowship of the Ring is revealed as the noble heir to the throne of the Kings of Men. Yet, the sole hope for triumph over evil lies with a brave hobbit, Frodo, who, accompanied by his loyal friend Sam and the hideous, wretched Gollum, ventures deep into the very dark heart of Mordor on his seemingly impossible quest to destroy the Ring of Power.​","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":23.6525,"vote_count":26076,"poster_path":"/rCzpDGLbOoPwLjy3OAm5NUPOTrC.jpg","release_date":"2003-12-17","vote_average":8.494,"backdrop_path":"/2u7zbn8EudG6kLlBzUYqP8RyFU4.jpg","original_title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King","original_language":"en"},{"id":123,"adult":false,"title":"The Lord of the Rings","video":false,"overview":"Young Hobbit Frodo Baggins is thrown into an amazing adventure when he's tasked with destroying the One Ring, created by the dark lord Sauron. Frodo must travel in a small fellowship of nine warriors and accomplices. But it won't be an easy journey for the Fellowship of the Ring, on the ultimate quest to rid Middle-earth of evil.","genre_ids":[12,16,14],"popularity":2.9408,"vote_count":1023,"poster_path":"/liW0mjvTyLs7UCumaHhx3PpU4VT.jpg","release_date":"1978-11-15","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/TXSxV23MWYkezZ3219gtgcSX6n.jpg","original_title":"The Lord of the Rings","original_language":"en"},{"id":271,"adult":false,"title":"Ronia: The Robber's Daughter","video":false,"overview":"Ronia lives happily in her father's castle until she comes across a new playmate, Birk, in the nearby dark forest. The two explore the wilderness, braving dangerous Witchbirds and Rump-Gnomes. But when their families find out Birk and Ronia have been playing together, they forbid them to see each other again. Indeed, their fathers are competing robber chieftains and bitter enemies. Now the two spunky children must try to tear down the barriers that have kept their families apart for so long.","genre_ids":[12,18,14,10751],"popularity":2.8965,"vote_count":193,"poster_path":"/gatMa1qfwpJqiawPjJxodUvdB0.jpg","release_date":"1984-12-14","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/lPYts3qpBDMlJaGjzd7nA5Piyd2.jpg","original_title":"Ronja Rövardotter","original_language":"sv"},{"id":272,"adult":false,"title":"Batman Begins","video":false,"overview":"Driven by tragedy, billionaire Bruce Wayne dedicates his life to uncovering and defeating the corruption that plagues his home, Gotham City.  Unable to work within the system, he instead creates a new identity, a symbol of fear for the criminal underworld - The Batman.","genre_ids":[18,80,28],"popularity":12.5976,"vote_count":22282,"poster_path":"/sPX89Td70IDDjVr85jdSBb4rWGr.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-10","vote_average":7.721,"backdrop_path":"/9IIBboV7MCT0bTxzXHmWK1Hq558.jpg","original_title":"Batman Begins","original_language":"en"},{"id":285,"adult":false,"title":"Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End","video":false,"overview":"Captain Jack Sparrow is trapped in Davy Jones' Locker when his pirate brethren begin a desperate quest to locate and rescue him. Follow their wild seafaring adventures from exotic Singapore to World's End and beyond.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":12.849,"vote_count":15233,"poster_path":"/jGWpG4YhpQwVmjyHEGkxEkeRf0S.jpg","release_date":"2007-05-19","vote_average":7.267,"backdrop_path":"/1jHxkVXMI5s3vRiyiZooUy1shB5.jpg","original_title":"Pirates of the Ca